template.basic-object: - Hides field if the value repeats on the next record (PRODUCTVENDOR)
- Conditionally set background color based on thresholds (QUANTITYINSTOCK)
- For Excel Output, it breaks on PRODUCTLINE and sets the Sheet name to PRODUCTLINE
- Applied a hyperlink to the PRODUCTNAME that searches PRODUCTNAME image on Google.com
- Localizable Reports, EntityTitle, reportTitle and dateTitle values come from a resource file
